<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-1090] Document the generation of a file called &quot;Constants.java&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1090</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A file called &quot;Constants.java&quot; is generated per thrift file that includes any constants. This should be documented somewhere because if you have multiple thrift files sharing the same namespace there will be clashes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(there is no &quot;documentation&quot; component so feel free to adjust those)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12501333">THRIFT-1090</key>
            <summary>Document the generation of a file called &quot;Constants.java&quot;</summary>
